    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "This shield is grown entirely of specially treated fungi, giving it the appearance of a frilly disc.  \nWhen left atop at least 1 bulk of organic matter, it gains fast healing 1; after 10 minutes 1 Bulk of the organic matter has been consumed by the shield. This shield doubles its hardness against bludgeoning, electricity, and sonic damage.",
